name: PegJS
body:
# peg-solitaire Peg solitaire game (HTML + JS)

Popular game Peg Solitaire, developed with HTML and Javascript.


Clone:
**`git clone https://github.com/ggades/peg-solitaire.git`**
Install dependencies for grunt:
**`npm install`**
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
